tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE operational_data (
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  parameter1 INT,
  parameter2 DECIMAL,
  data_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE business_data (
  business_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  revenue DECIMAL(10, 2),
  expenses DECIMAL(10, 2),
  profit DECIMAL(10, 2),
  date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE customer_feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  satisfaction_rating INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Operations (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    operation_name TEXT,
    operation_date DATE,
    operation_duration INTERVAL,
    operation_status TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Analytics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    operation_id INT,
    analysis_date DATE,
    analysis_result TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (operation_id) REFERENCES Operations(id)
);

CREATE TABLE BusinessProcesses (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    process_name TEXT,
    process_start DATE,
    process_end DATE,
    process_owner TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE operational_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    operation_name VARCHAR(50),
    data_value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE decision_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    decision_date DATE,
    decision_description TEXT,
    decision_made_by VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE process_optimization (
    optimization_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    optimization_date DATE,
    process_name VARCHAR(50),
    optimization_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE business_metrics (
    metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    metric_name VARCHAR(50),
    metric_value FLOAT,
    metric_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE transactions (
 transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 user_id INT,
 amount DECIMAL,
 transaction_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE users (
 user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 user_name VARCHAR(50),
 registration_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE products (
 product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 product_name VARCHAR(50),
 category VARCHAR(50),
 price DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE orders (
 order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 user_id INT,
 product_id INT,
 order_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE analytics_data (
 record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 data_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
 analysis_result JSON
)
